high_descs: Turn to the left and then face the stove on the right.
Pick up the bowl from the counter, to the left of the stove.
Carry the bowl and turn around, then face right to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the bowl.
Hold the bowl full of water and turn to the right to go to the stove.
Open the microwave and place the bowl inside, shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Fill up a bowl of water and heat it.

high_descs: Walk over to the stove and turn to face it.
Pick up the dirty bowl off of the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Put the dirty bowl in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the clean bowl of water.
Walk back over to the stove and look up at the microwave.
Put the clean bowl of water in the microwave and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl of water in the microwave.

high_descs: Go left and the turn to the right and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the bowl up from the counter.
go to the left and stand facing the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the bowl back up again.
Go right and face the microwave above the stove.
Put the bowl in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl in a microwave.
